{"id": 1127, "genre": 1000, "title": "你都看腻了哪些电影宣传套路？", "description": "宣传期，一个好多牛在天上飞的时间段。（题图来自：Julien Croyal）", "record_count": 9426, "comment_count": 29, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160724185301ynNIg8K1A2j0bLGR.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-07-24T17:00:11Z", "questions": [{"id": 1008, "title": "你都看腻了哪些电影宣传套路？", "content": "你都看腻了哪些电影宣传套路？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 100378, "content": "含有“大型”“巨作”字样的往往预告片比电影好看", "image": "img/option/option/20160721223643xOQUXiKcbJEkje60.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 100377, "content": "含有“史诗”字样的通常逻辑掉线", "image": "img/option/option/201607212247573eK1HFESf4No5qBc.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 100376, "content": "含有“知名IP”字样的往往毁原著不倦", "image": "img/option/option/20160721224016zG61VZFs54YjPrh8.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 100375, "content": "以“青春片”为宣传点多半狗血", "image": "img/option/option/201607212239402etJUoDdISri7LjC.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 100373, "content": "说自己“可以媲美周星驰”的通常都不怎么好笑", "image": "img/option/option/201607212247463yZAh5Q7G21aPikX.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 100371, "content": "捆绑男女主角炒 CP 的爱情片通常没有爱", "image": "img/option/option/20160721224917CpoPjnVMGN57U9v4.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 100370, "content": "打着“异国爱恋”旗号的就像旅游宣传片", "image": "img/option/option/20160721224958ZOv278JCx0DTudoP.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 100369, "content": "说自己“X年磨一剑”剧情可能单薄到你犯尴尬癌", "image": "img/option/option/20160721224523egKPko6XWjI3rdAt.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 100368, "content": "“颠覆之作”可能是“颠覆（三观）之作”", "image": "img/option/option/20160721224324Snom6rJ2KapZigEC.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 100367, "content": "“特效团队来自好莱坞”通常只花了七毛钱", "image": "img/option/option/201607212249041vKZEl7AHaDsRyOT.g